    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n    Nauczymy się dzielić wielomiany - pisemnie. To dzielenie będzie dość podobne do dzielenia pisemnego liczb. Z tą różnicą, że będziemy dzielić potęgi \\(x\\)-a.\n</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n    Żeby się do tego dobrze przygotować, powtórzymy:\n</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<ol class=\"bold\">\n<li>\n<a href=\"#dzielenie_pisemne_liczb\">\n            dzielenie pisemne liczb\n        </a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"#dzielenie_mnozenie_poteg\">\n            dzielenie i mnożenie potęg\n        </a>\n</li>\n</ol>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<h3 id=\"dzielenie_pisemne_liczb\">\n    Dzielenie pisemne liczb\n</h3>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p class=\"example\">\n</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n        Obliczymy razem pisemnie \\(745:6\\).\n    "
    },
    {
      "type": "spoiler",
      "label": "rozwiązanie",
      "body": "\n\n<div class=\"steps\">\n<p>\n                Zapiszmy działanie pod kreską:\n            </p>\n<div class=\"table_wrapper\">\n<table class=\"my_table_noborder\">\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                            \\(\\)\n                        </td>\n<td>\n                            \\(\\)\n                        </td>\n<td>\n                            \\(\\)\n                        </td>\n<td>\n                            \\(\\)\n                        </td>\n<td>\n                            \\(\\)\n                        </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                            \\(7\\)\n                        </td>\n<td>\n                            \\(4\\)\n                        </td>\n<td>\n                            \\(5\\)\n                        </td>\n<td>\n                            \\(:\\)\n                        </td>\n<td>\n                            \\(6\\)\n                        </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p>\n                Rozpatrujemy kolejne cyfry liczby \\(745\\), od lewej.\n            </p>\n<div class=\"show_next ks_button\">\n                pokaż dalej\n            </div>\n<div class=\"show_step\">\n<p>\n                    Najpierw\n                    <strong>\n                        dzielimy\n                    </strong>\n                    \\(7\\) przez \\(6\\). Szóstka w siedmiu mieści się \\(1\\) raz.\n                </p>\n<div class=\"table_wrapper\">\n<table class=\"my_table_noborder\">\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(7\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(:\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"show_next ks_button\">\n                pokaż dalej\n            </div>\n<div class=\"show_step\">\n<p>\n                    Teraz\n                    <strong>\n                        mnożymy\n                    </strong>\n                    wynik (\\(1\\)) przez dzielnik \\(6\\) i zapisujemy rezultat pod siódemką:\n                </p>\n<div class=\"table_wrapper\">\n<table class=\"my_table_noborder\">\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(7\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(:\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"show_next ks_button\">\n                pokaż dalej\n            </div>\n<div class=\"show_step\">\n<strong>\n                    Odejmujemy\n                </strong>\n                i spisujemy kolejne cyfry.\n                <div class=\"table_wrapper\">\n<table class=\"my_table_noborder\">\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(7\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(:\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"show_next ks_button\">\n                pokaż dalej\n            </div>\n<div class=\"show_step\">\n<p>\n                    Zauważ, że to, co zrobiliśmy do tej pory, można ująć w trzech małych krokach:\n                    <strong>\n                        dzielimy-mnożymy-odejmujemy\n                    </strong>\n                    .\n                </p>\n<p>\n                    Będziemy te kroki powtarzać. Teraz znów\n                    <strong>\n                        dzielimy\n                    </strong>\n                    , nie \\(1\\) przez \\(6\\) (bo \\(6\\) w \\(1\\) się nie mieści), lecz \\(14\\) przez \\(6\\).\n                </p>\n<p>\n                    \\(6\\) w \\(14\\) mieści się \\(2\\) razy.\n                </p>\n<div class=\"table_wrapper\">\n<table class=\"my_table_noborder\">\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(7\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(:\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"show_next ks_button\">\n                pokaż dalej\n            </div>\n<div class=\"show_step\">\n<p>\n                    Znów\n                    <strong>\n                        mnożymy\n                    </strong>\n                    (\\(2\\cdot 6=12\\)).\n                </p>\n<div class=\"table_wrapper\">\n<table class=\"my_table_noborder\">\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(7\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(:\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"show_next ks_button\">\n                pokaż dalej\n            </div>\n<div class=\"show_step\">\n<p>\n<strong>\n                        Odejmujemy\n                    </strong>\n                    (\\(14-12\\)).\n                </p>\n<div class=\"table_wrapper\">\n<table class=\"my_table_noborder\">\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(7\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(:\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"show_next ks_button\">\n                pokaż dalej\n            </div>\n<div class=\"show_step\">\n<p>\n<strong>\n                        Dzielimy\n                    </strong>\n                    (\\(25:6\\)).\n                </p>\n<div class=\"table_wrapper\">\n<table class=\"my_table_noborder\">\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(7\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(:\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"show_next ks_button\">\n                pokaż dalej\n            </div>\n<div class=\"show_step\">\n<p>\n<strong>\n                        Mnożymy\n                    </strong>\n                    (\\(4\\cdot 6=24\\))\n                </p>\n<div class=\"table_wrapper\">\n<table class=\"my_table_noborder\">\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(7\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(:\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n</td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"show_next ks_button\">\n                pokaż dalej\n            </div>\n<div class=\"show_step\">\n<p>\n<strong>\n                        Odejmujemy\n                    </strong>\n                    (\\(25-24=1\\)).\n                </p>\n<div class=\"table_wrapper\">\n<table class=\"my_table_noborder\">\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(7\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(:\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                                \\(6\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(5\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid black;\">\n<td>\n</td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(2\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(4\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"red_on_yellow\">\n                                \\(1\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"show_next ks_button\">\n                pokaż dalej\n            </div>\n<div class=\"show_step\">\n<p>\n                    Na dole zostało \\(1\\), i w tej liczbie dzielnik \\(6\\) już się nie mieści.\n                </p>\n<p>\n                    Wyszło nam\n                </p>\n                \\[\n                745:6=124\\tfrac{1}{6}\n                \\]\n                albo\n                <div class=\"centered\">\n                    \\(745:6=124\\) reszty \\(1\\)\n                </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<h3 id=\"dzielenie_mnozenie_poteg\">\n    Dzielenie i mnożenie potęg\n</h3>"
    },
    {
      "type": "spoiler",
      "label": "przypomnienie",
      "body": "\n\n<div class=\"important\">\n        \\[\n        \\begin{align*}\n        x^n\\cdot x^k&amp;=x^{n+k}\\\\\n        x^n: x^k&amp;=x^{n-k}\n        \\end{align*}\n        \\]\n    </div>\n<div class=\"important\">\n        Rozpatrzmy dwa wyrazy z potęgą \\(x\\):\n        <div class=\"centered\">\n            \\(Ax^n\\) oraz \\(Bx^k\\)\n        </div>\n        gdzie\n        <ul class=\"nolist\">\n<li>\n                \\(A\\) i \\(B\\) to pewne rzeczywiste, niezerowe współczynniki, a\n            </li>\n<li>\n                \\(n\\) i \\(k\\) to naturalne wykładniki potęg \\(x\\)-a.\n            </li>\n</ul>\n        Wówczas\n        \\[\n        \\begin{align*}\n        (Ax^n)\\cdot (Bx^k)&amp;=ABx^{n+k}\\\\\n        (Ax^n): (Bx^k)&amp;=\\tfrac{A}{B}x^{n-k}\\\\\n        \\text{to drugie łatwiej zapamiątać}&amp;\\\\\n        \\text{w postaci ułamków:}&amp;\\\\\n        \\frac{Ax^n}{Bx^k}&amp;=\\frac{A}{B}x^{n-k}\n        \\end{align*}\n        \\]\n    </div>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p class=\"question\">\n</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n        Wskaż wyniki następujących działań.\n    "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\\(3x^4\\cdot x^2=\\)</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    \\(3x^8\\)\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    \\(3x^6\\)\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    \\(9x^8\\)\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    \\(9x^6\\)\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    zatwierdź\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\\(4x^2\\cdot 3x=\\)</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    \\(12x^3\\)\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    \\(12x^2\\)\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    \\(7x^2\\)\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    \\(7x^4\\)\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    zatwierdź\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\\((6x^5):(2x)=\\)</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    \\(3x^4\\)\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    \\(4x^4\\)\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    \\(3x^5\\)\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    \\(4x^5\\)\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    zatwierdź\n                "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\\((8x^6):(4x^3)=\\)</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n                    &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                "
    },
    {
